{"tid":1795264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"會參加和你shop既求你地入黎","createTime":"2019-12-23T18:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T18:05:32.000Z","uid":335530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1707ac74b9d6831c993c99e8ed4a7a7cdbc8d8","tid":1795264,"uid":335530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:05:32.000Z","msg":"你話我左膠又好乜都好 如果個商場係塞爆人 求下手足你地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好裝修任何野</span></span> 有少數派過黎騷擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好私了</span></span> 一旦出左事 啲黑警就會明正言順入黎打人拉人 塞爆左個商場唔購物 其實已經達成左經濟攬炒呢個目的 可能你會話一定有鬼搞事 咁都請大家制止佢地 可以和平請大家一定要和平解決  手足拉一個少好多 唔好為左爆幾塊玻璃推幾張枱櫈換幾個手足比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非行動聚唔到人 咁就裝修完就閃交個場比警渣清<br />\n千奇千奇唔好有事冇事去爆美心爆吉記 <br />\n記住我地個目標係令到商場無生意做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np牌仔希望大家睇完可以幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望和你shop會大成功<br />\n<br />\n[行動] [推上熱門] 我宣佈 聽日平安夜攬炒正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}